{"tid":855974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文囑香港借鑒台灣追求民主","createTime":"2018-10-10T10:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T15:51:41.000Z","uid":20058,"like":116,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6661d64709bbf5a2b56bfc50c60040e304faea12","tid":855974,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"【蔡英文批大陸打壓民主燈塔】<br />\n【囑香港借鑒台灣追求民主】<br />\n <br />\n台灣舉行「雙十節」慶祝活動，總統蔡英文在講話中，批評大陸打壓台灣，強調台灣絕不讓步，但亦不會走向衝突對抗。<br />\n <br />\n「不會背離民意，犧牲台灣的主權。再次呼籲北京當局，一個負責任的大國，應該在區域及全球，扮演良性的角色，而不是衝突的來源。」<br />\n <br />\n她形容台灣猶如一座民主燈塔，叫香港、追求民主的朋友「往台灣方向看過來」。<br />\n <br />\n#有線新聞　#台灣　#icablenews　#hknews　#cablenews　#newsdaily　#news　#蔡英文　#台灣主權　#民主燈塔　#民主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2029230047134017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2029230047134017%2F&d=mbpCeGZ7F5pg7ap3sWC%2FOgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c8b97558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2029230047134017/</a>"},{"pid":"daace95a2524edce205e526b44ea2eaf7852cfda","tid":855974,"uid":19278,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d2490a04193b6fdd7ce9f006aa751db7f95c6e","tid":855974,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":80,"score":-73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"你地民主又點？有一萬億咩？垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4632f04f87d0c77d49f908698f281c609b2eb44f","tid":855974,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會又比支那批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a4f0c1bfe46bc9758dcc7069a2769ecbc8c629","tid":855974,"uid":24853,"like":37,